room_title: Escape room "Last Stop" by Red Door Escape Room in Oklahoma City
room_description: On a foggy night, a cold murder took place in an alley under the L Train. We need you and your team of private investigators to ID the victim, figure out the time of death, what the murder weapon was, and the motive behind it all... Oh, and one more thing - find the culprit! You only have 25 minutes to crack this mysterious case before the feds take it away. Remember, not everything can be seen at night. Good Luck!
